  "slug": "where-did-money-is-hard-come-from-journal",
  "title": "Where did \"money is hard\" come from?",
  "subtitle": "A journalling set for tracing the belief that earning requires struggle.",
  "excerpt": "A journal prompt set for examining the hard-earning belief: where it came from, who modelled it, whether it was ever true, and what a lighter version of earning might look like for you. Five prompts, twenty to thirty minutes.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Drawn from The Money Journal: 12 Weeks to Peace, Freedom & Overflow (Rebecca J Page, 2025), Week 2 prompts on breaking generational money patterns.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal set for tracing the hard-earning belief back to its source. Five prompts. Allow twenty to thirty minutes.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journalling as a practice? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What does earning currently feel like in your body?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Heavy, light, neutral, anxious? Write what's true right now, not what should be.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Did anyone in your family make earning look easy? Or was it always shown as a struggle?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Name the person and the picture you have of them and money.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where did the belief that money is hard to earn first land?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A specific memory, a phrase overheard, a lesson taught directly. Write what you find.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Is that belief still serving you? Name one way it protects you and one way it costs you.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Both sides exist. Write both.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What would you charge, take, or accept if you believed earning could be lighter?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "One specific thing. Name the number or the opportunity.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Drawn from The Money Journal: 12 Weeks to Peace, Freedom & Overflow (Rebecca J Page, 2025), Week 2.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
